data.description: Calling all Investors!! This is your next Flip. Need a little TLC to shine again. This a 3 bedrooms & 3 full baths with master bedroom on main level. This home has a finished basement, 2 additional rooms can be used as bedrooms.  A lot of space, mud room laundry next to kitchen, 2 attached auto garage, front porch, plus a walkout den to the open view back deck. Huge out building for more storage space. Priced to sell! This rare gem won't last. SOLD AS-Is
